    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a ninja cat, you must parkour across the map to collect croissants. BUT avoid falling into the water! Your cat hates that… This game is a fast-paced, family-friendly parkour adventure — perfect for playing with family and friends online!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer:</strong> Compete against other online cats to collect croissants. The first cat to collect 3 croissants win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single-player:</strong> Race against time in single-player to collect the croissants without dying, and become the best on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a family-friendly game to emphasize cats acting in fun parkour to collect croissants. More maps are planned to be released in the future.</p>",
